Most of the CCTV Camera output format as DAV files. Using ffmpeg we can convert Convert DAV format to Mp4 format. The ffmpeg already a "Multiprocessing" one. 


# Steps to run the Script:

1. Install ffmpeg for Ubuntu

```
For Ubuntu 
``` 
sudo apt-get update

sudo apt install ffmpeg

ffmpeg -v
```
2.Just put DAV files in DAV2MP4 directory.

3. Run the "python3 dav2mp4_im.py" file.If you have bigger file, surely it takes time.
